    • Constructor Detail

      • DataSourceInstance

        public DataSourceInstance(String entitySourceId,
                          String entitySourceDescriptor,
                          String datasetName)
        Creates a new DataSourceInstance for the entity with the source id "entitySourceId" based on the dataset with the provided name "datasetName" which is an instance of the source with the provided name "sourceType".
        Parameters:
        entitySourceId - the id of the entity in the source system (i.e. how is the instance identified in the source)
        entitySourceDescriptor - the name/descriptor of the field that was used as sourceId (i.e. how can i find the id in the source)
        datasetName - the name of the dataset, e.g. edx_dalmooc_20150202

      • DataSourceInstance

        Creates a new DataSourceInstance for the entity with the source id "entitySourceId" based on the dataset with the provided name "datasetName" which is an instance of the source with the provided name "sourceType".
        Parameters:
        entitySourceId - the id of the entity in the source system (i.e. how is the instance identified in the source)
        entitySourceDescriptor - the name/descriptor of the field that was used as sourceId (i.e. how can i find the id in the source)
        sourceType - the name of the source system (e.g. edX, prosolo, wikipedia)
        datasetName - the name of the dataset, e.g. edx_dalmooc_20150202
